@page "/data-deletion"
@{
  ViewData["Title"] = "Data Deletion — Queenzone";
  ViewData["Description"] = "How to request deletion of your personal data from Queenzone.";
  ViewData["CanonicalPath"] = "/data-deletion";
}

<partial name="_PageHero" model='@(("Your Data", "Data Deletion", "How to request removal of your personal information from Queenzone.", "Last updated 2 July 2026"))' />

<section class="qz-section qz-section--warm">
  <div class="qz-container" style="max-width: var(--container-text);">

    <p class="lede">You can request that we delete your personal data at any time. Here's how.</p>

    <h2>What we store</h2>
    <p>If you have a Queenzone account, we store your email address, display name, and (where applicable) a reference to the social login provider you used (Google or Microsoft). We do not store passwords in plain text.</p>

    <h2>How to request deletion</h2>
    <p>Send an email to <a href="mailto:privacy@queenzone.org">privacy@queenzone.org</a> with the subject line <strong>"Data Deletion Request"</strong> and include the email address associated with your account. We will process your request within 30 days and confirm by email once complete.</p>

    <h2>What gets deleted</h2>
    <p>We will delete your account and the personal information associated with it (email address, display name, social login references). Public content you posted (such as forum posts) may be anonymised rather than deleted to preserve archive integrity, unless you specifically request otherwise.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For any questions about your data, email <a href="mailto:privacy@queenzone.org">privacy@queenzone.org</a>.</p>

  </div>
</section>
